TITLE: Workflow with Multiple Suspension Points TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates a workflow with multiple steps, each with the capability to suspend based on specific conditions.  It showcases how to use the `suspend` function with optional payload data.  The workflow is then constructed using `Workflow` and chained `step` and `then` methods, representing the execution flow with suspension points.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mastra-ai/mastra/blob/main/docs/src/content/en/docs/workflows/suspend-and-resume.mdx#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
