TITLE: Mapping Data Between Steps (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to map data from the output of one step (`generateData`) to the input of another step (`processData`).  The `previousValue` input of `processData` is populated with the `nested.value` property from the output of `generateData`. Requires `@mastra/core` and `zod`.
