TITLE: Upsert Embeddings into Astra DB with Mastra (TSX)
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to create a collection and upsert embeddings into DataStax Astra DB (a cloud-native vector database) using the `AstraVector` class from the `@mastra/astra` package.  It relies on the `openai` package for creating embeddings and `MDocument` from `@mastra/rag` for handling text chunks. The `ASTRA_DB_TOKEN`, `ASTRA_DB_ENDPOINT`, and `ASTRA_DB_KEYSPACE` environment variables are required for database authentication.
