TITLE: Define Candidate Workflow - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Defines the overall candidate workflow by chaining the defined steps and implementing branching logic based on the candidate's technical status. It first gathers candidate information, then asks about the specialty if the candidate is technical, or asks about the role if the candidate is not technical.  Uses the `when` condition to define the branching logic.
