TITLE: Performing Vector Search and Re-ranking with Mastra
DESCRIPTION: Executes a vector search on the stored embeddings and re-ranks the results using Mastra's rerank function, combining vector similarity, semantic relevance, and position scores.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mastra-ai/mastra/blob/main/docs/src/content/ja/examples/rag/rerank/rerank.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
