TITLE: Workflow.while() with Reference Condition
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use a reference condition with comparison operators to control the `.while()` loop.  The `ref` object specifies the step and path to a value, and the `query` object defines the comparison operator and target value. Requires a workflow, `incrementStep`, `finalStep`, and a step that produces a result with a 'value' property.
