TITLE: Create Research Assistant Agent (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Creates a RAG-enabled research assistant agent using @mastra/core.  It utilizes a Vector Query Tool for semantic search and GPT-4o-mini for generating responses. The agent is configured with specific instructions for analyzing papers and using retrieved content. Dependencies include @mastra/core/agent, @ai-sdk/openai, and @mastra/rag.
