TITLE: Using LibSQLVector for Vector Storage
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to use the `LibSQLVector` class to create, manage, and query vector embeddings. It includes creating a new vector store instance, creating an index, adding vectors with metadata, and querying similar vectors with optional metadata filtering.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mastra-ai/mastra/blob/main/docs/src/content/ja/reference/rag/libsql.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
