TITLE: Evaluating Low Faithfulness Response with Mastra
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code snippet illustrates the process of evaluating a response with low faithfulness using Mastra's FaithfulnessMetric. It defines a context, initializes the metric, provides a query, and a response that contradicts the context. The code then prints the results of the metric evaluation, demonstrating how low faithfulness scores are generated and the reasons behind them.
