TITLE: useChat Hook Implementation - TypeScript (Component)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the usage of the `useChat` hook from `@ai-sdk/react` in a React component. The component handles chat interactions by managing messages, input, and form submission. The `api` property in `useChat` should point to an API endpoint that handles agent stream requests. This allows for real-time chat interactions in a frontend application.
