TITLE: Creating and Storing Embeddings
DESCRIPTION: This snippet generates embeddings for the document chunks and stores them in the vector database. It uses the `embedMany` function to create embeddings using the OpenAI embedding model, creates an index in the vector store, and upserts the embeddings and metadata into the vector store. The dimension of the embedding is set to 1536.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mastra-ai/mastra/blob/main/docs/src/content/ja/examples/rag/usage/cot-rag.mdx#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
