TITLE: Integrating with an Agent
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to integrate memory processors with an agent. It sets up a `Memory` instance with a `ToolCallFilter` and `TokenLimiter`, then creates an `Agent` with the processed memory. The agent uses the memory to retain context during conversations.
