TITLE: Branching and Merging Paths in Mastra Workflows (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to create branching and merging paths in a Mastra workflow.  stepA branches into stepB and stepC. stepB leads to stepD, and stepC leads to stepE. stepF is only triggered after both stepD and stepE are complete.
