LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
myWorkflow
  .step(stepA)
    .then(stepB)
    .then(stepD)
  .after(stepA)
    .step(stepC)
    .then(stepE)
  .after([stepD, stepE])
    .step(stepF);
```

